snippet.title: Roof Rage - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Roof Rage, a platform fighter featuring epic martial arts battles on rooftops, is now available on Nintendo Switch !

Battle with up to 8 players locally or solo in the arcade mode to try to unlock the boss in this fast-paced brawler.

Find your main player among 13 characters, each one offering a unique playstyle.

Roof Rage available now! http://bit.ly/32u8y7t

#RoofRage #NintendoSwitch
